2.10	Manabu_Yukawa	Manabu Yukawa	Manabu Yukawa is a fictional character from Keigo Higashino Galileo series. He features in the books Tantei Garireo, Yochimu, The Devotion of Suspect X, Seijo no Kyusai and Garireo no Kuno currently. He also appears in the Japanese television drama, Garireo as well as the movie, The Devotion of Suspect X. Both are portrayed by Masaharu Fukuyama and are very popular in Japan. Yukawa is a genius but eccentric physicist. He is often approached by his old school mate, who is currently a detective, to solve the seemingly supernatural and impossible cases.	
